nodes.text: Taisden was a New Republic officer onboard the Glorious. When Colonel Ejagga Pakkpekatt volunteered to search for Lando Calrissian, Lobot, C-3PO and R2-D2; Taisden, along with Pleck and Bijo Hammax, volunteered as well. Needless to say, they succeeded with the help of Jedi Master Luke Skywalker.
